entries.s_32: You're the one Inquisitor Loam sent? Finally. The courier has gone into hiding. He wouldn't explain why, but I know where he is. Hopefully you can talk some sense into him.
entries.s_34: Inquisitor Redge is bound to send someone soon. I hope so, I feel exposed standing out here.
